28 providing:
29 (A) A signed form stating the blood type of the person;
30 and
31 (B) Payment of the fee for the driver's license or
32 identification card authorized under this chapter.
33 (2) If the person seeks a duplicate or substitute driver's
34 license with the blood type designation and his or her driver's license has
35 not expired, the fee shall be as provided under ยง 27-16-806.
36 (b) The Office of Driver Services may:
